# Keep the book PDF out of source archives.
#
# GitHub builds release zipballs with `git archive`, which honors export-ignore.
# Zenodo archives that zipball. The PDF in book/ is the author's pre-edit draft,
# posted with SIAM's *conditional* permission and withdrawn when copy-editing begins.
# A Zenodo deposit is permanent and immutable, so the PDF must never enter one.
#
# The companion materials (MIT-licensed) are what the DOI is for.

book/*.pdf export-ignore
